         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">17/8/92 ¶  ¶ With much regret, dear and honored Sir, I feel myself discapacitated from attending the Concert, to which you so kindly invited me, and which is sure to be a great treat! ¶ 'The first of ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">92.08.17</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Thomas Sisley</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RB MSS M1, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">17/8/92</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>With much regret, dear and honored Sir, I feel myself discapacitated from attending the Concert, to which you so kindly invited me, and which is sure to be a great treat!<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>'The first of the three farewell concerts of M. Ovide Musin and his gifted collaborateurs<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>took place last night in the Town Hall' (Argus, 18 August 1892, p. 7).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>But I suffer from a severe bronchial catarrh, so much so, that during last night I had hardly any sleep from continuous coughing, and thus I am afraid to go out into the cold night-air. Let me hope, that I can enjoy your next musical soiree, when the weather will be warmer also.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Please accept the bye-following portrait<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Troedel &amp; Co's portrait of M;<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>see<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <ref target="http://handle.slv.vic.gov.au/10381/299306">http://handle.slv.vic.gov.au/10381/299306</ref>.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>of which I received several impressions from a lithographic friend.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Perhaps some of your friends and yourself will honor us with your presense at the next Concert of the Melb Liedertafel.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Regardfully</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd von Mueller<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS annotation by Sisley on a blank sheet with MS: 'Baron Von Mueller. 17/8/92. Answered'. Letter not found.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
         </div>
